Class Grade

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.edu.agh.jdziennik.model.Grade

  • @Entity
public class Grade
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a grade given to a student. This class is mapped by hibernate.

      • Grade

        public Grade(Student student,
             ClassSubject classSubject,
             Grade.GradeValue gradeValue,
             GradeType gradeType,

        Creates new Grade using the values passed. Also generates a timestamp based on the current system time. Sets references to and from student and lesson. The newly created object does not have id set.
        Parameters:
        student - the student
        classSubject - the class subject
        gradeValue - the grade value
        gradeType - the grade type
        comment - Should be allowed to be null (this needs fixing)
